description.narrative:
The overall objective of the contribution is to consolidate the democratic character of the relationship between the citizens and the government in security-related issues in Serbia, including the integration of a gender perspective.
This objective will be addressed through four sets of activities/result areas:
Result 1: Implementation of personal data protection legislation is strengthened, with particular focus on the security sector;
Result 2: Good governance in the security sector is further promoted;
Result 3: Participation of civil society in the democratization of the security sector is further strengthened;
Result 4: Education and expertise in the security sector is further advanced.
